<subSubSection id="C34F64FB556FFF83528DB936FB25FD35" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BEA3770556FFF83528DB936FDADFDC2" blockId="5.[189,535,559,585]" box="[189,535,559,585]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<heading id="D0A2801C556FFF83528DB936FDADFDC2" bold="true" box="[189,535,559,585]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B921EB62556FFF83528DB936FDADFDC2" bold="true" box="[189,535,559,585]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Distribution and bionomics</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEA3770556FFF83528DB944FB25FD35" blockId="5.[189,1399,605,702]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
The representatives of the new subtribe are distributed in the deserts of Central and South Asia (
<collectingCountry id="F34277E0556FFF8352F5B999FED6FD11" box="[197,364,640,666]" name="Turkmenistan" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Turkmenistan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F34277E0556FFF83534AB998FE16FD10" box="[378,428,641,667]" name="Iran" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Iran</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F34277E0556FFF835388B999FDF0FD11" box="[440,586,640,666]" name="Afghanistan" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Afghanistan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F34277E0556FFF835068B999FD04FD11" box="[600,702,640,666]" name="Pakistan" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F34277E0556FFF8350FDB999FCA3FD10" box="[717,793,640,667]" name="China" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">China</collectingCountry>
): Karakum, Dasht-e Lut, Dasht-e Kewir, Registan, Taklamakan. Species of the mentioned genera inhabit non-fixed barchan sand dunes.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C34F64FB556FFF83528DB9FCFD26FCDA" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BEA3770556FFF83528DB9FCFEE3FD74" blockId="5.[189,345,741,767]" box="[189,345,741,767]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<heading id="D0A2801C556FFF83528DB9FCFEE3FD74" bold="true" box="[189,345,741,767]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B921EB62556FFF83528DB9FCFEE3FD74" bold="true" box="[189,345,741,767]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Comparison</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEA3770556FFF83528DB80DFD26FCDA" blockId="5.[189,1399,788,849]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
The subtribe 
<taxonomicName id="4C554CF3556FFF835355B80DFCF4FCA5" authority="Nabozhenko &amp; S. Chigray" authorityName="Nabozhenko &amp; S. Chigray" authorityYear="2022" box="[357,846,788,814]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subTribe" status="subtrib. nov." subTribe="Habrobatina">Habrobatina Nabozhenko &amp; S. Chigray</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A2125619556FFF83516CB80DFC4EFCA5" box="[860,1012,788,814]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" rank="subTribe">subtrib. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
can be distinguished from the nominotypical one by the following key:
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C34F64FB556FFF83528DB861FCA9FC19" box="[189,787,888,914]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" type="multiple">
<paragraph id="8BEA3770556FFF83528DB861FCA9FC19" blockId="5.[189,787,888,914]" box="[189,787,888,914]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
